room_title: Escape room "The Deadwood Saloon" by Masterpiece Escapes in Charlotte
room_address: 14015 E Independence Blvd Indian Trail, NC 28079
room_description: The old Deadwood Saloon belonged to my great uncle Cyrus. He was a master with his maps and pickaxe, the saloon holds all his secrets to the early 1800s Carolina Gold Rush. The Deadwood Saloon is in an area that time forgot and we have all the time in the world to discover the secrets that it holds. Good luck and be careful!
